Author: XBrick_Exchange
Title: XBrick.io to officially open its Bitcointalk Account
Body: XBrick.io is a secure and reliable global crypto currency exchange, began operating on 11 November 2017.  Sign up at https://www.xbrick.io/r.html  Why Are We Different?    XBrick is an Exchange and also a selective Tokensale Distribution Channel. To bring on new projects, we will engage the community to find, to debate and to vote on them!  Management then steps in to performs legals on selected projects!    Why Should You Hang Around?  XBrick is proud to launch our Platform Token - XBrick Coin (XBC)!  Registered users may go to XBrick Coin (XBC) main website xbc.xbrick.io and submit an Expression of Interest.  We really appreciate the long term support from you, XBrick is soon to launch our newly developed Global Consolidated Order Book, through our internally developed Dynamic-Liquidity-Providing-Engine (DLPE) we will gather liquidity globally to fill your trade on XBrick, the system will also close the price gaps through execution on XBrick.  We look forward to go a long way with you!  Airdrops and Candy programs will be here soon!  Those who are registered and KYC compliant Users on xbrick.io will enjoy many potential Goodies!    Our X-STRATEGY:  XBrick began running on November 11 2017. Throughout the last 4 months we have received and accepted many valuable feedbacks from our registered Users!  From this point XBrick is setting a TINY TARGET:  by June 30 2018 let’s rise KYC-passed Users over 250,000!  Once this number is reached XBrick will unleash its self developed Global Consolidated Order Book (GCOB) and Dynamic Liquidity Providing Engine (DLPE) to our System! We give all users a REASON to TRADE with us accessing to the best comparable PRICES and the WORLD’s LIQUIDITY!  Becoming A Professional With XBrick!
